# Normalize line endings. Without this, Windows checkouts convert LF→CRLF
# in the working tree (driven by core.autocrlf=true) and `git status` lights
# up every TS file as modified every time it's touched. Storing LF in the
# repo and LF in the working tree keeps diffs clean on every platform.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files that must not be normalized.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
*.zip binary
*.tar.gz binary
